{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard\f0 If \b Selected\b0 , it will be possible to update the current set of data processing purposes.\par
\b\f0 WARNING:\b0\f0  Once confirmed, this option might result in irreversible data removal or data anonymization.\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard\f0 If \b Selected\b0 , all purposes for storage and processing of personal data will be withdrawn.\par
\b WARNING:\b0  Once confirmed, this option will result in irreversible data removal or data anonymization.\f0\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard\f0 The date \f0 until\f0  which the purpose for storing personal data is valid.\par
\f0\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard\f0 If \b\f0 selected\b0\f0  and the information refers to an action of updating purposes in the \b\f0 Update History\b0\f0  table, the purpose for processing personal data is valid.\par
If \b\f0 selected\b0\f0  and the information refers to an action of data erasure in the \b\f0 Update History\b0\f0  table, the purpose for processing personal data has been withdrawn.\par
